'''Deakis Ronse''' was a professor of cosmology with the [[University of Sanbra]]. He and other [[Scientist/Legends|scientists]] analyzed the chromospectra of the [[Star/Legends|star]] [[Demophon (star)|Demophon]], predicting a [[Supernova/Legends|supernova]] within the next 50 [[Standard year/Legends|standard years]].

